title: SilverSun Pickups Acoustic Set
description:
This is a set of acoustic songs from SilverSun Pickups. Featuring Brian Aubert and Nikki Monninger. This album was edited and compiled by me from good quality acoustic performances sourced from various locations.

1. Well thought out Twinkles Acoustic
2. Future Foe Scenarios Acoustic
3. Waste it on Acoustic
4. Lazy Eye Acoustic
5. Rusted Wheel Acoustic
6. Common Reactor Acoustic
7. Kissing Families Acoustic
8. Creation Lake Acoustic
9. Shadowplay Acoustic

folder.jpg

Enjoy SSPU fans.
